 - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -   Hi Frank & All,  Hmmm?! I thought all one has to do was remove the Mute pin! Now, you say I&#39;ve got to look at the revese side from where the pin was and cut(!?) or undo (somehow) a wire that that pin connects to?  If I do all this the right way, how does the radio work/sound,then?  I&#39;m confused, at this point. I also can plug in external, but small, speakers rather than use the earbuds.  =Judy= P.S. How can I tell if a pin has shorted??       . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .
